t not always, the Genuine Orders were =E2=80=9Ciceberg=E2=80=9D orders, so =
that other market participants could see only a portion of the order=E2=80=
=99s full size at any given time. An =E2=80=9Ciceberg=E2=80=9D order was a =
type of order that a trader could place on certain trading platforms and ex=
