eciates 20% against the dollar in the same period, the Treasury -- that is,=
 taxpayers -- would pay deposit-holders the differential. The instrument wi=
ll apply for individuals holding lira deposit accounts with maturities betw=
een three to 12 months. The minimum interest rate will be the central bank=
=E2=80=99s benchmark rate and no withholding tax will be implemented.</p></=
blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">To get the benefit you have to lock=
 up your money for at least three months, and there are <a href=3D"https://=
link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26137490.286658/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyL=
mNvbS9jYW5va2FyL3N0YXR1cy8xNDczMjU3MTc3Mjg0NDkzMzE5/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23=
