text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-c=
olor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">might n=
ot work</a>!</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A third way to think of it is =
that it=E2=80=99s just a bank account with a variable interest rate.=C2=A0T=
raditionally the way you do monetary policy is that when inflation is high =
and your currency is losing value, you raise interest rates, so people have=
