ccounts rather than spending it on food or dollars. You set the interest ra=
te at some number, and if the currency keeps falling you raise the number, =
and eventually you reach an equilibrium (you hope!). Turkey=E2=80=99s appro=
ach is to set the interest rate at a variable, the variable being =E2=80=9C=
however much the currency falls.=E2=80=9D Again the goal is to reach the eq=
uilibrium quickly =E2=80=94=C2=A0if people say =E2=80=9Cah well this will a=
lways be worth a dollar=E2=80=9D and don=E2=80=99t sell, you don=E2=80=99t =
actually have to pay out much =E2=80=94=C2=A0though apparently another goal=
 is to avoid=C2=A0<em>saying=C2=A0</em>that Turkey is raising interest rate=
s.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But my brain has been broken by years of=
 writing about crypto, and my first thought was=C2=A0=E2=80=9Cah yes it=E2=
