color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">of aro=
und 5,200%</a>. Higher than the lira!</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">When =
I first read this explanation in <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/26137490.286658/aHR0cHM6Ly9kb2NzLm9seW1wdXNkYW8uZmluYW5jZS9t=
YWluL2Jhc2ljcy9iYXNpY3M/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB312428b7" itemprop=3D"Stor=
yLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; t=
ext-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-co=
lor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">the Olym=
pusDAO documentation</a>, I laughed and laughed. =E2=80=9CWell yes right,=
