y fiat currency; it is particularly saliently true of the lira right now, b=
ut if everyone sold their dollars to buy euros (or Bitcoins, or OHM), that =
would be bad for the dollar too. =E2=80=9CThe value of a currency depends o=
n its widespread social acceptance, though it=C2=A0can be influenced in the=
 short term by the interest rate that you can get in that currency=E2=80=9D=
